{"tid":489909,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"雙雄之爭－爛番茄評分榜嚴選 20 部史上最佳英雄電影","createTime":"2017-12-05T07:02:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T16:14:19.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ebda65a2461e0cfb9241d60c5c8bb6b8f86521cb","tid":489909,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:02:45.000Z","msg":"爛番茄（Rotten Tomatoes）的評分榜一直被批評為毫無公信力的指標，縱使由網站計算的 Tomatometer 指數理想也不代表電影票房成績優異，反之亦然。有見及此，Quartzy 綜合了爛番茄的官方（Tomatometer）及觀眾評分（Audience Score），嚴選出電影史上 20 部得分最高的英雄電影。穩佔榜首位置的電影為官方及觀眾評分均達至 94 分的《The Dark Knight》，其於 2012 年推出的續集《The Dark Knight Rises》亦一同上榜，以 87 及 90 分穩守第 16 位。其他上榜電影還有《Iron Man》、《Logan》、1978 版本的《Superman》和《Spider-Man》等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hypebeast.imgix.net/https%3A%2F%2Fhk.hypebeast.com%2Ffiles%2F2017%2F12%2Frotten-tomatoes-20-best-superhero-movies_2.png?auto=compress%2Cformat&amp;fit=max&amp;ixlib=php-1.1.0&amp;q=90&amp;w=1600&amp;s=c07302dead2b7f10ffbdcb5db31afa07\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.imgix.net%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fhk.hypebeast.com%252Ffiles%252F2017%252F12%252Frotten-tomatoes-20-best-superhero-movies_2.png%3Fauto%3Dcompress%252Cformat%26fit%3Dmax%26ixlib%3Dphp-1.1.0%26q%3D90%26w%3D1600%26s%3Dc07302dead2b7f10ffbdcb5db31afa07&h=92de70e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/rotten-tomatoes-20-best-superhero-movies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2017%2F12%2Frotten-tomatoes-20-best-superhero-movies&d=u6jx%2F9VOFGkjBxnBGyTxeaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=9dfcef1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/rotten-tomatoes-20-best-superhero-movies</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://quartzy.qz.com/1143813/the-all-time-greatest-superhero-movies-ranked-by-rotten-tomatoes/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fquartzy.qz.com%2F1143813%2Fthe-all-time-greatest-superhero-movies-ranked-by-rotten-tomatoes%2F&d=u6jx%2F9VOFGkjBxnBG